===Noun===
'''guys''' ''plural''

#Plural of [[guy]].
# (''colloquial'') Persons, irrespective of their genders.
#:''Who are those '''guys'''?''
# (''colloquial'') A form of address for a group of male persons or a group of mixed male and female persons.
#:''Hi '''guys'''!''

